         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Order change requests may arise due to factors such as requested delivery date (RDD), pricing, quantity, ship-to address, Incoterm, payment terms, etc.</text>
